Why aren’t you hustling?

CEOs on LinkedIn would really like to know.
(Not because they care — but because they need to humble-brag about working on Sundays.)

In today’s episode of Corporate Fan Fiction, we break down LinkedIn’s favorite genre:
“I worked while you were living your life.”

Featuring:
CEOs “finding clarity” on Sundays… at the office
Executives posting workout routines longer than most workdays
Hustle posts that sound like satire but unfortunately aren’t
Coffee counts that should require FDA approval
Open offices
title: CEOS "HUSTLE-FLEXING" ON LINKEDIN LIKE NEVER BEFORE
